  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.poster.avif?t=1762537545\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.webm?t=1762537545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.mp4?t=1762537545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW FAST CAN YOU GO ?</h2><strong>Challenge your friends in an endless run!</strong><br>Up to 4 players with a single keyboard or 4 controllers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/44bffefee42477d6d00d6ff50adc6762.webp?t=1762537545\" width=129 height=51 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GOAL IS SIMPLE</h2> <strong>Tap the only button as fast as you can to move and stay on screen</strong>. If you get off screen, you will lose. The last Blobi standing wins the Game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/c155109fd84f1504293b7fb2ab95c679.apng?t=1762537545\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/c155109fd84f1504293b7fb2ab95c679.poster.avif?t=1762537545\" class=\"bb_img\" width=100 height=150 /></picture></span><br><br>Features :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2-4 Players<br></li><li>1 Button<br></li><li>1 Level<br></li><li>1 Goal<br></li><li>1 Winner!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING : Fast tapping for survival can be very exhausting!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.poster.avif?t=1762537545\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.webm?t=1762537545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/cece9e058cc2a9e60df70f45472ea3cd.mp4?t=1762537545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW FAST CAN YOU GO ?</h2><strong>Challenge your friends in an endless run!</strong><br>Up to 4 players with a single keyboard or 4 controllers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/44bffefee42477d6d00d6ff50adc6762.webp?t=1762537545\" width=129 height=51 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GOAL IS SIMPLE</h2> <strong>Tap the only button as fast as you can to move and stay on screen</strong>. If you get off screen, you will lose. The last Blobi standing wins the Game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/c155109fd84f1504293b7fb2ab95c679.apng?t=1762537545\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270960/extras/c155109fd84f1504293b7fb2ab95c679.poster.avif?t=1762537545\" class=\"bb_img\" width=100 height=150 /></picture></span><br><br>Features :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2-4 Players<br></li><li>1 Button<br></li><li>1 Level<br></li><li>1 Goal<br></li><li>1 Winner!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING : Fast tapping for survival can be very exhausting!</h2>",
